<div>
  <div class="text-center pt-2">
    <h1>Tens a certeza que queres<br> uma nova companhia?</h1>
    <p>Responde a este inquérito para avaliarmos se tem o que é<br> preciso para adotar um novo companheiro.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="pt-5 d-flex gap-3">
    <div>
      <form action="/adopt/form" method="post" class="fs-5">
        <div>
          <label for="age" class="form-label">Data de nascimento</label>
          <input type="date" class="form-control form-bar rdo-style" id="age" name="age" required>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-4">
          <label for="nif" class="form-label">NIF</label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control pt-2 form-bar" id="nif" name="nif" required>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-4">
          <label for="address" class="form-label">O seu endereço</label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control pt-2 form-bar" id="address" name="address" required>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-4">
          <label for="postal_code" class="form-label">Código postal</label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control pt-2 form-bar" id="postal_code" name="postal_code" required>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-4">
          <label for="locality" class="form-label">Localidade</label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control pt-2 form-bar" id="locality" name="locality" required>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-4">
          <label for="phone" class="form-label">Contacto telefónico</label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control pt-2 form-bar" id="phone" name="phone" required>
        </div>
        
        <div class="pt-4">
          <h2>Contribuições / Apoios</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-4">
          <div><label>Financeira</label></div>
          <div class="form-check form-check-inline pt-2">
            <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="costs" id="costs" value="option1">
            <label class="form-check-label" for="costs">Semanal</label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
            <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="costs" id="costs" value="option2">
            <label class="form-check-label" for="costs">Mensal</label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
            <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="costs" id="costs" value="option2">
            <label class="form-check-label" for="costs">Anual</label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-4">
          <label for="value" class="form-label">Valor</label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control pt-2 form-bar" id="value" name="value" required>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-4">
          <div><label>Investimento</label></div>
          <div class="form-check form-check-inline pt-2">
            <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="investment" id="investment" value="option1">
            <label class="form-check-label" for="investment">Passeios</label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
            <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="investment" id="investment" value="option2">
            <label class="form-check-label" for="investment">Fins de semana</label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-check form-check-inline pt-2">
            <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="investment" id="investment" value="option1">
            <label class="form-check-label" for="investment">Divulgação do animal</label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
            <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="investment" id="investment" value="option2">
            <label class="form-check-label" for="investment">Vacinação</label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-check form-check-inline pt-2">
            <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="investment" id="investment" value="option1">
            <label class="form-check-label" for="investment">Tratamentos</label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
            <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="investment" id="investment" value="option2">
            <label class="form-check-label" for="investment">Tosquia</label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-check form-check-inline pt-2">
            <input class="form-check-input rdo-style" type="radio" name="investment" id="investment" value="option1">
            <label class="form-check-label" for="investment">Outra</label>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="pt-4">
          <p>Para efetuar o pagamento pode fazer depósito, transferência bancária ou pagamento por MBWAY:<hr>
             IBAN: PT50XXXXXXXXXXXXX<hr>
             MBWAY: 91xxxxxxx </p>
        </div>

        <div class="form-check pt-4">
          <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" value="" id="defaultCheck1" required>
          <label class="form-check-label" for="defaultCheck1">
            Autorizo a utilização dos dados inseridos, em conformidade com a Política de Privacidade
          </label>
        </div>
            
            <div class="text-center pt-4">
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Enviar</button>
            </div>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="card" style="width: 16rem;">
          <img src="/images/logo/dog.svg" class="card-img-top" alt="logoDog">
          <div class="card-body text-end">
            <h4><%= animal_name_date.name %></h4>
            <h5><%= animal_name_date.birth_date.toLocaleString("pt-PT") %></h5>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
</div>

<style>
  .form-bar{
    width: 50rem;
    height: 2.5rem;
    background-color: rgba(29, 29, 27, 0.11);
    border-radius: 2rem;
  }

  .rdo-style{
    background-color: rgba(29, 29, 27, 0.11);
  }

</style>